### Auth API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5122
@contentType = application/json

### Sign Up - Create new account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test.employee@company.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123",
  "confirmPassword": "TestPassword123",
  "fullName": "Test Nhân Viên",
  "employeeCode": "EMP001",
  "phoneNumber": "+84912345678"
}

###

### Login - Authenticate user
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test.employee@company.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123"
}

###

### Get Current User Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.idToken}}
###

### Verify Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-token
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

"{{login.response.body.idToken}}"

###

### Sign Up - Invalid password match
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "invalid@company.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123",
  "confirmPassword": "DifferentPassword",
  "fullName": "Invalid User",
  "employeeCode": "EMP002",
  "phoneNumber": "+84912345679"
}

###

### Sign Up - Missing required fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/sign-up
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "incomplete@company.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123"
}

###

### Login - Wrong password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test.employee@company.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

###

### Login - Non-existent user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nonexistent@company.com",
  "password": "AnyPassword123"
}

###
